text: "Rio" is the seventh single by English new wave band Duran Duran and is the title track to their second album. It went to number 3 in Canada, number 9 in Ireland and the United Kingdom and number 14 in the United States. It was first released in Australia in August 1982. ==References== Category:1982 songs Category:Duran Duran songs Category:Moby songs
